OL,6,FServing police officers on the day of
OL,7,Fthe Omagh bombing described the
OL,8,Faftermath of the atrocity as "hell on
OL,9,Fearth".
OL,11,FThere was a "smell of death" one
OL,12,Fpolice officer who responded to the
OL,13,Fblast recalled.
OL,15,FTwenty-nine people, including a woman
OL,16,Fpregnant with twins, were killed when
OL,17,Fthe Real IRA detonated a car bomb in
OL,18,Fthe Co Tyrone town.
