OL,3,COmagh bomb aftermath 'hell on earth,'
OL,4,Csays police officer
OL,6,FPhilip Marshall, who was duty sergeant
OL,7,Fat the Omagh police station on the day
OL,8,Fof the bombing, said it had been an
OL,9,Fotherwise ordinary and "beautiful day"
OL,10,Fprior to the bomb warnings with
OL,11,Fofficers preparing for a carnival to
OL,12,Fpass through the town.
OL,14,FHe said he would come to regret the
OL,15,Ftraffic plan initiated for the parade
OL,16,Fas it involved deploying traffic
OL,17,Fwardens to an area of the town that
OL,18,Fwould be affected by the eventual
OL,19,Fbombing.
