OL,3,COmagh bomb aftermath 'hell on earth,'
OL,4,Csays police officer
OL,6,FMr Marshall, who retired after just
OL,7,Funder 30 years of service in 2009 with
OL,8,Fthe rank of chief inspector, said he
OL,9,Fwas told at around 2.30pm the police
OL,10,Fstation had received a bomb warning
OL,11,Fthat used a recognised codeword that
OL,12,Fhad been cited in previous incidents.
OL,14,FHe said he immediately tasked officers
OL,15,Fto begin clearing the town centre,
OL,16,Ffocused around the area of the
OL,17,Fcourthouse, which had been mentioned
OL,18,Fin the warning. He travelled to the
OL,19,Farea himself in a marked car.
