OL,6,FFurther warnings were issued but Mr
OL,7,FMarshall said none of them contained
OL,8,Fany information on the car's
OL,9,Fregistration, make, model, colour or
OL,10,Fexact location.
OL,12,F"If we had got any of that, we
OL,13,Fwouldn't be sitting here today," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
