OL,3,COmagh bomb aftermath 'hell on earth,'
OL,4,Csays police officer
OL,6,F"The first thing that hits you was the
OL,7,Fnoise, you had all the shop burglar
OL,8,Falarms going, you had a horrendous
OL,9,Famount of screaming, there was also a
