OL,12,Fbeen involved in evacuating people
OL,13,Faway from the area of the courthouse
OL,14,Fwhere the bomb call related to.
OL,16,F"Many of those people evacuated made
OL,17,Ftheir way down Market Street to the
OL,18,Fvery site of the bomb blast and some
OL,19,Fwere either fatally or seriously
OL,20,Finjured.
