OL,6,FMr Baxter concluded: "The impact of
OL,7,Fthe bomb and subsequent events on my
OL,8,Fwellbeing were such that I cut my
OL,9,Fpolice career short and left in 2003."
OL,11,FAnother police officer who spoke to
OL,12,Fthe inquiry on Tuesday described how
OL,13,Fhe tried to help victims in the scenes
OL,14,Fof devastation which followed the
OL,15,Fexplosion.
OL,17,FAllan Palmer, an RUC constable in
OL,18,F1998, told the Omagh Bombing Inquiry
OL,19,Fon Tuesday that he remembered seeing
OL,20,Fpeople lying dead in front of him in
OL,21,Fthe moments following the blast.
