OL,6,FA statement from Mr Palmer was read to
OL,7,Fthe inquiry. It said he was on duty in
OL,8,Fthe Co Tyrone town in August 15 1998,
OL,9,Fwhen he was notified of a bomb alert
OL,10,Ffor near the town's courthouse.
OL,12,FHe said he directed traffic away and
OL,13,Fbegan to evacuate pedestrians and shop
OL,14,Fowners away from the area.
OL,16,FHe said pedestrians were moved towards
OL,17,Fthe bottom of Market Street, where the
OL,18,Fcar containing the bomb had been left.
