OL,6,FMr Palmer said: "As we continued to
OL,7,Fmove down Market Street the bomb
OL,8,Fexploded.
OL,10,F"All I can recall is a flash of light,
OL,11,Fa great suction and a sharp piercing
OL,12,Fpain in my back.
OL,14,F"At the moment the bomb exploded I was
OL,15,Fa short distance away and shards of
OL,16,Fglass from the shop windows fell into
OL,17,Fmy back."
