OL,6,FHis statement said: "I will never
OL,7,Fforget the horror of what I witnessed
OL,8,Fat the scene of the Omagh bomb.
OL,10,F"The memories and emotions that I
OL,11,Fcarry with me every day are too many
OL,12,Fto include in this statement.
OL,14,F"The horrors, the guilt, the
OL,15,Fhelplessness, the anger, the hurt and
OL,16,Fmore have all had a serious impact on
OL,17,Fboth my physical and psychological
OL,18,Fhealth.
